{"tid":1127474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"債台高築、賣血維生... 中國「強制脫貧」逼貧民上絕路","createTime":"2019-04-27T06:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T09:24:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"364ba9bd5466f8eafb88c90a4bdd7ad29efd5faa","tid":1127474,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/04/27/phpB0EuvI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2FphpB0EuvI.jpg&h=c5db581e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平自十八大上任以來，就訂下2020年全面脫貧的目標，中國官媒紛紛為其政績歌功頌德，但實際上，地方政府採取各種荒唐手段讓當地貧困戶「強制脫貧」，使得貧困戶債台高築，更有九旬老人因此被逼死。<br />\n<br />\n《寒冬》報導，中國當局採取荒唐的手段，強行封堵老年貧困戶的房屋，強迫他們與兒女同住，就宣稱那些貧困戶老人「被脫貧」了。河南省商水縣譚莊鎮某村在今年2月21日，村民發現一名九旬老人在自己的小屋裡已經過世，這名老人並非正常死亡，當地政府人員為實現脫貧定額，強制要求老人與子女住在一起，以便讓上級檢查。村民透露，當地幹部曾多次要求老人與子女同住，但老人與兒子產生矛盾，覺得壓抑痛苦，就又搬回自己的小屋住，之後老人就被發現在屋中自盡。<br />\n<br />\n報導提到，中國當局的「扶貧」政策不但沒有讓人民擺脫貧困，還讓他們負債累累，生活更加拮据，甚至還有人靠賣血維生。河北省的一位農民，丈夫臥病在床，一兒一女也都有病，2016年被列入貧困戶，但當地政府為了達成「有房住」的脫貧標準，多次逼他們搬離窯洞，住進新房，但新房連門窗都沒有，根本沒辦法入住，也無法承擔高額的裝修費，政府仍然強制執行，讓她在醫療費和裝修費上兩頭燒，沒有拿到任何補助，她生病的丈夫只好瞞著家人偷偷去賣血，被迫「脫貧」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2772181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2772181&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=c11c089b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2772181&h=ebc987a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2772181</a>"},{"pid":"27cf69125fc4dece83f68700132904c4027fe7d3","tid":1127474,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:48:25.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3f790d2b5d04c38af91d229f14f1d71cd73afdbd","tid":1127474,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:49:20.000Z","msg":"中國紅十字會香港分部叫大家無償'獻'血喎"},{"pid":"0235a5b19af50edcb94995545b397d3d993c1511","tid":1127474,"uid":56957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:49:50.000Z","msg":"地獄"},{"pid":"43547d6d470c80365b0be8dcd585a0994556684a","tid":1127474,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:50:25.000Z","msg":"如果解決不了問題<br />\n就解決提出問題的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32e82b913f4a499c72e6a657b90ba41f81cd144","tid":1127474,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/02/27/draft/5980447.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F02%2F27%2Fdraft%2F5980447.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=9ebc66be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39482ad068ea92148c82002e8fdb387f8afce956","tid":1127474,"uid":84585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:51:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f3059671d1bf3954eb01c09003bc90f4202749c","tid":1127474,"uid":49979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:52:51.000Z","msg":"好想知d愛國人士會點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16039c4be9ec98a090247fd6fca7049882d0c885","tid":1127474,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:56:17.000Z","msg":"沒有中國解決唔到嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n因為無問題"},{"pid":"4979650fd8396ed83479409b5f984b49eee6bc91","tid":1127474,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T07:21:49.000Z","msg":"習總要2020全國小康<br />\n班官為左交數乜都做得出"},{"pid":"d05cb50a58fff0860c4bd6c70da8c19636a5ced9","tid":1127474,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4f3059671d1bf3954eb01c09003bc90f4202